  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3357476">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3357476/" class="title-link">绘画如何抵抗？</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3357476"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/vangoghsmood/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1263625-94.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/vangoghsmood/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">vangoghsmood</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-06-25"
      class="main-meta">2010-06-25 13:20:00</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3357476_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                       “被画，即是被看见。”     我这样理解约翰伯格所言的可见物。     不是说照相机般的复制，或者用眼角的斜扫，经过，但不被看见。           “这个秘密就是我进入我在观看的任何东西里面。”     所言即是画家对自己所绘之物的看，是目光交汇，灵魂交流，画家放弃自己的...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">4有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_3357476_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_3357476_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










